'''Christopher Malcolm''' ([[August 19]], [[1946]] - [[February 15]], [[2014]]) was a Scottish actor, director, and producer known for his work in the musical [[Wikipedia:The Rocky Horror Show|''The Rocky Horror Show'']] the [[1986]] films [[Wikipedia:Highlander (film)|''Highlander'']] and [[Wikipedia:Labyrinth (1986 film)|''Labyrinth'']]. He played the [[Rebel pilot]] [[Zev Senesca]] in the [[1980]] [[original trilogy]] film, [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']].

